{
  "stem": "14156.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But after that, I ended up in Bologna and, from there, went into Reggio Emilia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I was-- I was ill, and I was-- I was treated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- a doctor treated me, with my illness, being-- having pleurisy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, in-- in-- in the city, he put me up on this table, and he said, take off the shirt.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Took a needle that long and went in between the ribs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And took-- without anaesthesia-- anything-- and took-- took the fluid out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, after that, I was, like, a new man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or a kid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I recovered, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there, the British had this-- it was under British control, that Reggio Emilia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every time the British came in, the officers and the sisters there, the nurses, they pointed to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know him?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a skeleton.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Look at him now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was eating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was eating maybe too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Didn't do anything, just laying around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At night you used to go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or visit other places who are-- who were-- what should I say?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I was a virgin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to go try it-- try out how it feels to be with a woman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I went there, too, so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after that, we were told-- we went to another city, not far away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one day we were there, we were told, get ready.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Take your shower now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And take whatever you can.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you're going to go to a special place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody ask.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wouldn't answer you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here comes about four or five trucks-- the tarpaulin down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they pushed us in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were you worried?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
